snippet.textDisplay: Why is vardys left foot only rated 3 stars on fifa. He scores a lot of good goals with his left foot, I think it was last season that he  even got goal of the season with a controlled left foot volley as the ball come over his shoulder. Its clear to see that hes actually left and right footed which is why I think he manages to score a lot of goals with not many shots. Unlike a lot of strikers he doesn't try and switch the ball onto a preferred foot  meaning he doesn't waste any time.
